Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Protecting the president
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w9jt
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 Apr 1981
Gun control and increased protection levels called for following Reagan assassination attempt. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less